FY 2025 Plans:
Funding is for the continued development of FETs. FAB-T FET integration and testing activities will include
reliability growth testing and fabrication of test assets; prototype and test terminals will support terminal security,
environmental, and functional testing, to include flight testing, and early integration efforts.

Planning and support activities will continue, including qualification test planning, logistics support planning, risk
reduction activities for development and follow-on production, technical analysis and studies, platform integration
support, program office support, and mitigations for Diminishing Manufacturing Sources and Material Shortages
in preparation for terminal production.
