C. Other Program Funding Summary ($ in Millions)
Remarks
Program funding has been transferred between this Project and other DAF Projects and this current Project does not represent the full investment. Additional details can
be discussed under separate cover.

D. Acquisition Strategy
The DoD led Moving Target Indicator project partnered with the NRO to leverage efficiencies and completed market research informing the Analysis of Alternatives
identifying vendors capable of meeting technical and schedule requirements. The project will award Firm Fixed Price contracts that leverage a low-risk approach by
leveraging mature commercial technologies to accelerate the acquisition timeline and meet the GMTI needs of the warfighter. Competition will be maintained through
technical maturation of an alternate vendor that will be later down selected to award development and delivery of the second block of space vehicles.




