A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
In FY 2026, Project 673942, Joint Commercial Operations (JCO) efforts were transferred from Project 673940, Space Data Fusion to increase transparency.
In FY 2026, Project 673943, Space Domain Awareness Network (SDANet) efforts were transferred from Project 673940, Space Data Fusion to increase transparency.

