environments to address all aspects of flight and robust mission performance. Develop technologies for advanced control-
enabled capabilities, including flight controls, components, integrated vehicle management systems, and software and system
certification techniques to enable Autonomy Technology Development for Autonomous Collaboration and affordable mass,
including usage of a Government Reference Architecture.

