- Continue evaluation of DoW inventions and intellectual property and facilitation of T2 agreements, focusing on license
agreements and CRADAs around dual use technologies.
- Continue expanding nationwide marketing program to further engage the industrial base around T2 partnership opportunities.
- Stop training and education efforts of new stakeholder and topic-based training modules.
- Stop recurring assessments of the economic and warfighter impacts of DoW T2 activities.
