strategy. The approach for the Ensemble Analysis for HDBT defeat: 1) Synthesize current state-of-the-art, including past research and validated capability requirements,
2) Conduct a holistic study to examine and recommend solutions for all dimensions of HDBT defeat considering nuclear, conventional, and non-kinetic effects, to
include layering of two or more of those effects, and 3) inform and drive follow-on AoAs to provide concrete trade space characterization and acquisition strategy
recommendations for each of the three effect categories.

