engineering and technical management expertise required in monitoring critical areas of nuclear weapons safety, security, cyber,
reliability, operations, modernization, testing, and counterproliferation.

FY 2026 Plans:
• Complete: (1) Engineering implementation; (2) Cloud implementation sustainment; (3) Digital Engineering Pilot Project.
• Continue digital data standardization for digital systems engineering efforts.
• Continue to develop and provide common data models aligned to a center data strategy.


